"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640951138,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"4rHdI8La9HLagwO66S3q9xNz59NVpeyeAWD5B2g5b_g\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x386E635D5d30A269F1D3f0e5E5309Fd33049f72c\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2OTW5IplYguncBtvPzk2NfVPWO40o98xylw4dk0_auQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7fS02eAEbl6jhPkn5OFVhIMQ7-u1lgeXcfpS4_pJV04\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"01GRfzHRF_XSBCURDlL3f7GhyCk1SADYtqAAsnzw1ujgJ1wVbDLrKzjTiLgqWp3UNqVtWONUdNSlOxYozr4yRw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe95e2e9a89fb1ab64abcaaae1fbf29b640920d53a86723e740a19755d32be21d20856138464363c9e1033c842620edc712a4ffa85bbed1c463b1057d4fcf50ef1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2OTW5IplYguncBtvPzk2NfVPWO40o98xylw4dk0_auQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7fS02eAEbl6jhPkn5OFVhIMQ7-u1lgeXcfpS4_pJV04\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi